{"tid":1819904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 陳偉霆自爆戴阿媽胸圍","createTime":"2020-01-11T08:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T03:50:39.000Z","uid":71632,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0f49a36245a7b48cdbc959a630abb7fc05a1a825","tid":1819904,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】陳偉霆（William）昨與白韻琴、謝偉俊（阿Paul）出席奧海城的母親節活動，William戴上道具一嘗孕婦的辛勞，更首度嘗試冲奶粉及餵奶。談到扮孕婦可怕破壞靚仔形象？William笑說：「我行Cuite路線。（比阿Sa可愛？）當然不及她。」他還自爆日前試戴母親的胸圍，他說：「我一直做健身操胸肌，洗澡後赤裸上身問母親有否變化，母親笑說戴得到她的胸圍才叫大，說罷便拋了個胸圍過來，我便戴上給她看，當然我的胸是橫向發展，不及母親大。」活動後William便飛往杭州工作，對未能與媽咪慶祝母親節感可惜，他說：「有想過帶母親一同來活動慶祝，但她昨晚打完通宵麻將，所以還是免了。我想送她一張三萬元的按摩椅，她說折現便可以。」他又透露阿Sa亦不在港，女友回港後會先跟其母慶祝，稍後再與Sa媽補祝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200106_EN_%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E9%9C%86_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200106_EN_%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259C%2586_3.png&h=be37698a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200106_EN_%E9%99%B3%E5%81%89%E9%9C%86_2-e1578284171367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200106_EN_%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259C%2586_2-e1578284171367.jpg&h=07a17fb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"800dc0943feb090d90f659bd97e99a7107956d6d","tid":1819904,"uid":65984,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"成陣大陸味"},{"pid":"b48e6dc38ee66f66959f4a548f7e75e315b5c22d","tid":1819904,"uid":280136,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-mobile